* W02_seq_basic.sno - sequential pattern: two literals matched left-then-right
* Rung W02. E_SEQ: 'foo' 'bar' matches 'foobar'.

        subject = 'foobar'
        pat = 'foo' 'bar'
        subject pat              :f(e001)
        OUTPUT = 'PASS W02/001: seq match succeeded'         :(END)
e001    OUTPUT = 'FAIL W02/001: seq match should succeed'
END
